main event: A report detailing the observation of a UFO in Junauska, North Carolina, on March 30, 1967.
interesting points: The report includes two photographs of the UFO., The UFO is described as round and disk-shaped., The UFO is hovering over a landscape, possibly a field or open area., No human figures are visible in the images., The report is unclassified and belongs to the Foreign Technology Division, AFSC.
